{
  "stem": "10862.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She came home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was saved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father, he had a premonition that something was wrong.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he went out to-- to look for his child like any normal father would.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He paid for his with his life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, after the bombing was over, we went back to our house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we lived there for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very, very hard for my mom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I remember my sisters-- you know, when you don't have money and you don't have food, you will do anything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my sisters used to go to the to the street-- not streetcar-- to the railroad where they were bringing in coal.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we would steal the coal-- we would catch on the-- on the-- on the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, we would sell it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, of course, some of it we would keep in the house to keep us warm.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you would do all sorts of things, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother, somehow or other, tried to cope.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- we had very, very little food-- very little food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how I-- that's how we managed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at that time, my sisters still were going to school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Life turned to pretty normal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, of course, in 1940 again, that's when all the things started again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just a few months that things like that-- you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, till about half a year, I would say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- you know, I don't remember it clearly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I said, being that I was so young, I don't remember a lot of the things what exactly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can only remember that we were told that we had to move out of that area-- that we were being moved to a-- a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
